

Recipe from Naga 


1. Go to Grocery store 
2. Buy Pita bread,pizza sauce, mozzarella cheese, dried oregano leaves seasoning, choice of toppings (colored bell peppers, onions, olives, mushrooms,panner/chicken)
3. Once u have all ingredients ready.
4. Start preparing pizza :)
5.preheat oven 350 for 10 mins ahead
5. spread sauce to pita bread, add cheese, add toppings
6.put it on foil on aluminium tray & put in oven for 15-20 mins 
7. when u see cheese melted & bread crust turn little golden brown; you can turn it off after 15 mins 
8. Enjoy pizza <3; Party with family

STAY SAFE STAY HOME 
